Kirby, 1837: 52. Type locality: &quot;Lat. 54° [= along North Saskatchewan River]&quot; (original citation), restricted to &quot;Edmonton, Al[ber]ta&quot; by Lindroth (1963b: 328). Holotype [by monotypy] in BMNH (Lindroth 1953b: 176).
